But if the turnStrength is 5 and the wobble is 4*5=20 plus swirl 6*5=30, that's 50 units of perpendicular offset vs 25 units forward. The step direction changes by atan(50/25) ≈ 63 degrees. That's very sharp - almost a right-angle turn.

